name: GSI Complex with Dryer Function
description:
Just as the title says. GSI Complex with Dryer Function. This is a production system placeable. You have to enter the production chain menu and turn on the production point! (see picture)

 19381489 Liter capacity. Snow masks now added to the bins, dryer, fans etc. Holds all standard grain crop types. Animated doors, lights, dryer fans, and cover mat. See pictures for where to stand activate triggers. Error free other than a warning for shapes file size. Enjoy and please report any issues back to me! Credits to Ryan Kusumo Dhewanto for the bins and base dryer (both have been edited).
